<figure class="data-asset-lifecycle" aria-labelledby="data-asset-lifecycle-caption">
  <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__title">
    <span>VERSIONED DERIVATION GRAPH</span>
    <strong>每个在线结果都要能追溯、失效并重建</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__graph" aria-label="数据资产版本化派生图">
    <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__node">
      <small>SOURCE</small>
      <strong>来源版本</strong>
      <span>身份、授权、内容Hash、有效时间</span>
    </div>
    <span class="data-asset-lifecycle__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__node">
      <small>JOB</small>
      <strong>解析与规范化</strong>
      <span>代码/配置/环境版本</span>
    </div>
    <span class="data-asset-lifecycle__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__node">
      <small>DERIVED</small>
      <strong>Chunk / Feature</strong>
      <span>父版本、Schema、质量结果</span>
    </div>
    <span class="data-asset-lifecycle__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__node data-asset-lifecycle__node--published">
      <small>PUBLISHED</small>
      <strong>Index Generation</strong>
      <span>原子指针、可回滚版本</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="data-asset-lifecycle__changes">
    <div>
      <small>CHANGE</small>
      <strong>更新 / 删除 / 权限变化</strong>
      <span>先产生可审计事件，不直接散改每个派生存储。</span>
    </div>
    <span class="data-asset-lifecycle__down" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
    <div>
      <small>IMPACT</small>
      <strong>沿血缘计算影响集</strong>
      <span>定位需要失效、重算、撤回和清理的后代版本。</span>
    </div>
    <span class="data-asset-lifecycle__down" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
    <div>
      <small>CONVERGE</small>
      <strong>重建 → 验证 → 切换 → GC</strong>
      <span>查询只能看到一个完整Generation；旧版本按保留策略清理。</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <figcaption id="data-asset-lifecycle-caption">
    血缘不是展示图，而是更新、撤回、权限收紧与重建时计算影响范围的执行依据。删除源文件不等于删除了Chunk、Embedding、缓存和历史导出。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

